 //å®ä¹trialsï¼å®ä¹ææçæé®ååºï¼æ­£ç¡®çæé®ååºï¼åºæ¿åç°é¡ºåºç­ä¿¡æ¯
 ======================================================================================================================================================================
 <trial instruction>
 	/validresponse = (anyresponse)
 	/stimulusframes = [1=instructiontxt,anykeytxt]
 	/recorddata = false
 </trial>
 
 <trial same1trial>
 	/pretrialpause = 500
 	/validresponse = ("F","J")
	/correctresponse = ("F")
 	/stimulusframes = [1 = fixation;100=same1txt]
 </trial>
 
 <trial same2trial>
 	/pretrialpause = 500
 	/validresponse = ("F","J")
 	/correctresponse = ("F")
 	/stimulusframes = [1 = fixation;100=same2txt]
 </trial>
 
 <trial different1trial>
 	/pretrialpause = 500
 	/validresponse = ("F","J")
 	/correctresponse = ("j")
 	/stimulusframes = [1 = fixation;100=different1txt]
 </trial>
 <trial different2trial>
 	/pretrialpause = 500
 	/validresponse = ("F","J")
 	/correctresponse = ("j")
 	/stimulusframes = [1 = fixation;100=different2txt]
 </trial>
 
 //å®ä¹blocks,å®ä¹å±æ§ä¿¡æ¯ï¼å å¥trails
 ======================================================================================================================================================================
 <block instructionblk>
 	/screencolor = (0,0,0)
 	/trials = [1 = instruction]
 </block>
 

 <block stroopblk>
 	/screencolor = (0,0,0)
 	/blockfeedback = (meanlatency,correct)
 	/trials = [1-8 = noreplace(same1trial, same2trial,different1trial,different2trial)]
 </block>
 
 //å®ä¹experiment, å å¥blocks
 ======================================================================================================================================================================
 <expt>
 	/ blocks = [1 = instructionblk; 2 = stroopblk]
 </expt>


